## Executive Summary

The Challenge:
Implement recommendations from previous Memory System Overhaul:
✅ Automated SKILLS.md updates after each session
✅ Monitoring dashboard for system health
✅ Error tracking with auto-fix capabilities
✅ Routing feedback loop for improved accuracy

The Solution:
Created 4 new intelligent systems that work together:
Monitoring Service — Tracks metrics, logs, and alerts
Skills Manager — Automatically updates SKILLS.md based on session patterns
Error Tracker — Records errors, identifies patterns, suggests fixes
Routing Feedback — Learns from user feedback to improve agent routing

The Result:
✅ 19/19 tests passed (100%)
✅ Auto SKILLS.md updates implemented
✅ System monitoring with health checks
✅ Error pattern detection and auto-fix
✅ ML-enhanced routing with feedback loop

