## Auto-SKILLS.md Update System

### How It Works

Trigger: Session completion via /api/memory/enhanced

Process:
Session Logging → Log task and outcome to MEMORY.md
Error Analysis → Check for errors in session
Pattern Detection → AI analyzes for new patterns
Skills Update → Add/remove patterns in SKILLS.md
Validation → Ensure SKILLS.md format is correct
Monitoring → Record metrics and alerts

